snippet.title: The backrooms VR Co-op Multiplayer Wishlist trailer, PC Steam, Meta Quest 2, Sidequest
snippet.description:
Get it here:
Sidequest: https://sidequestvr.com/app/9937/the-backrooms-vr
AppLab: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/7619842234757409
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1931820/The_Backrooms_VR

Co-op up to 4 players!

Live the true Backrooms VR Experience in a psychological horror game, where you'll be alone in a liminal world full of entities that will hunt you at every moment, Scary, dark this immersive VR experience allows you to use your hands to grab and use items to solve puzzles inside this liminal world.
